=== Moderate ME/CFS
<subsec:moderate-mecfs>

*Functional Capacity.*

    - Unable to work full-time or maintain consistent employment
    - Housebound part of the time
    - Can perform some self-care but requires frequent rest
    - Severe reduction in activities compared to pre-illness
    - PEM more severe and prolonged

*Common Symptom Profile.*

    - Significant fatigue and PEM lasting days to weeks
    - Marked cognitive impairment
    - Moderate to severe pain
    - Orthostatic intolerance limiting upright time
    - Multiple sensory sensitivities
